arts.ttl: Steven Gerrard leaves Al Ettifaq after 18 months
arts.sum: Al Ettifaq confirm the departure of manager Steven Gerrard.

arts.ttl: Steven Gerrard breaks silence on Al Ettifaq exit as Rangers ally follows Liverpool icon out of the door
arts.sum: The former Rangers and Aston Villa boss leaves after a disappointing 18 month in the Saudi Pro League

arts.ttl: Gerrard out as Al Ettifaq boss after 18 months
arts.sum: Steven Gerrard has left his post as manager of Saudi Pro League side Al Ettifaq after 18 months with the team struggling in the bottom half of the table.

arts.ttl: Gerrard set to leave role as Al Ettifaq manager
arts.sum: Steven Gerrard is set to leave his role as Al Ettifaq manager after 18 months in charge of the Saudi Arabian club.
